Ext.data.JsonP['Appcelerator_Studio_Release_Notes']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Appcelerator Studio Release Notes</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-40929417\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Appcelerator Studio Release Notes</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-40929417_AppceleratorStudioReleaseNotes-Studio4.9.1.GA-3August2017\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Studio 4.9.1.GA - 3 August 2017</span></h2>\n    <p>Studio 4.9.1.GA  is a patch release that includes one new improvement and several bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-40929417_AppceleratorStudioReleaseNotes-Improvements\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvements</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8746\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8746</a> - Android: Studio should now use &apos;id&apos; for emulator instead of &apos;name&apos; when building for android emulator.    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>The AVD id for the emulator is now used instead of the name when building for Android    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-40929417_AppceleratorStudioReleaseNotes-Fixedissues\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed issues</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8776\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8776</a> - The Default Emulator or AVD drop down list in Android Preference page does not refresh after AVD creation    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8787\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8787</a> - Change &apos;Manage AVDs&apos; button text to &apos;Create AVDs&apos; while working with new Android SDK versions    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8791\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8791</a> - Diagnostic log: Sensitive environment variables included    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8794\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8794</a> - Studio dashboard page shows server unavailable due to invalid SSO url    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8795\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8795</a> - Update JDK 1.8 release notes text in the Studio updates dialog    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8806\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8806</a> - Filter out android-tv and android-wear on AVD creation window    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8820\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8820</a> - Create AVD window throws error in running avdmanager cmd on windows-10    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-40929417_AppceleratorStudioReleaseNotes-RecentReleases\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Recent Releases</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.9.1.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.9.1.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.9.1.RC_Release_Note\">Studio 4.9.1.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.9.0.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.9.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.8.1.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.8.1.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.8.0.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.8.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.8.0.RC_Release_Note\">Studio 4.8.0.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.8.0.Beta_Release_Note\">Studio 4.8.0.Beta Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.7.1.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.7.1.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.7.0.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.7.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.7.0.RC_Release_Note\">Studio 4.7.0.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.7.0.Beta_Release_Note\">Studio 4.7.0.Beta Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.6.0.GA_Release_Note\">Studio 4.6.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.6.0.RC_Release_Note\">Studio 4.6.0.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_4.6.0.Beta_Release_Note\">Studio 4.6.0.Beta Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Studio_3.1.3_Release_Note\">Studio 3.1.3 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=40929417\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Appcelerator Studio Release Notes"});